result.name: Hui Lau Shan

reviews.text: Dessert is average. When I asked for a cup of water to take my meds, the staff coldly answered no.

Despite it closes at 1130pm officially, the manager told us, unapologetically, that there is "no juice" (meaning they only sell prepared dessert, not freshly made juice I think) when we got there at 1050pm. They should change the official closing time to 1030pm instead. 未到十一点已經唔賣嘢,不如改為十点半收工！？

The desserts are really good, however, the service was really bad. I asked about order, because I was worried that she forgot my order. Then the lady waitress tell me it is coming in Cantonese with a rude tone and attidude.
Horrible service and uses microwave to heat up warm dessert and those desserts aren't in microwave-safe bowls
Not open I think closed

result.name: 許留山

reviews.text: 甜品以芒果為主，頗吸引吃甜品的愛好者; 燕窩椰王可算是許留山的「震山之寳」。週一至五營業時間:12:00-23:00、週六日及公眾假期:12:30-23:30。
Dessert is average. When I asked for a cup of water to take my meds, the staff coldly answered no.

Despite it closes at 1130pm officially, the manager told us, unapologetically, that there is "no juice" (meaning they only sell prepared dessert, not freshly made juice I think) when we got there at 1050pm. They should change the official closing time to 1030pm instead. 未到十一点已經唔賣嘢,不如改為十点半收工！？

The desserts are really good, however, the service was really bad. I asked about order, because I was worried that she forgot my order. Then the lady waitress tell me it is coming in Cantonese with a rude tone and attidude.

食品滿意。
地方淺窄，坐位空間有點擠逼，員工人數不足。
